additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Always read the label. Follow directions for use. Keep out of reach of children. Do not swallow. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Dispose of empty container with household rubbish. Store below 30C For advice contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26) or a doctor. If swallowed do not induce vomitting. Give a glass of water to drink. If skin contact occurs, wash thoroughly, if in eyes, wash out with large amount of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor.
